  "2403600": {
    "name": "Jamboy, a Jelly-cious Hero",
    "steam_appid": 2403600,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《Jamboy：果酱英雄》是一款充满活力的动作平台游戏，主角是一位非同寻常的果酱人。</strong><br>他似乎天生就有陷入黏糊糊麻烦的“天赋”，每次冒险都让人忍俊不禁。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏采用章节式短篇故事结构，融合多种游戏类型，带来令人着迷的玩法体验，绝对能牢牢抓住玩家的注意力。<br>再加上手绘风格的迷人美术和狡黠幽默的表现方式，整体氛围让人不禁联想到经典游戏《蚯蚓吉姆》的荒诞魅力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2403600/extras/8579f275af4c2675ec3fd3821e97a49f.webp?t=1758814196\" width=616 height=40 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2403600/extras/6b3e7594e31d2345dd9e0c36c8162a7c.poster.avif?t=1758814196\" width=700 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2403600/extras/6b3e7594e31d2345dd9e0c36c8162a7c.webm?t=1758814196\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Jamboy和Billy正疯狂逃离一只穷追不舍的警察甜甜圈！<br>在回顾一连串糟糕的决定后，他们竟然被一个意想不到的角色吞噬了——Damien！Damien是谁？原来是一个体型巨大的家伙，刚好挡在他们的逃跑路线上。太倒霉了……谁让他们没睁大眼睛看路！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这场离奇事件之后，Jamboy被迫进入巨人的体内深处。一个由食物怪物盘踞的迷宫般通道正等待着他。虽然这场“肉洞探险”是意外开启的，但想要逃出去，可是一场技巧与智慧的终极考验！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2403600/extras/12f84b3cb0297a1c9f39b4555750b36e.webp?t=1758814196\" width=616 height=40 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2403600/extras/c4a105f6f89db680b468b9e83d6b4bba.poster.avif?t=1758814196\" width=700 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2403600/extras/c4a105f6f89db680b468b9e83d6b4bba.webm?t=1758814196\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>故事模式</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Jamboy被困在一场消化系统的混乱之中，只有你才能帮助他逃脱。Snack模式提供轻度难度，专为游戏新手或喜欢轻松体验的玩家设计。而Buffet模式则是完整的Jamboy体验，挑战逐步升级，敌人各具特色，适合经验丰富的玩家。无论你选择哪种模式，都将踏上一段充满平台跳跃、幽默感与意外事件的冒险旅程。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>失落关卡</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >想要更多？完成主线战役后，你将解锁全新的挑战关卡，专为考验你的技巧并拓展游戏体验而设计。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>附加内容</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Jamboy还有更多精彩内容！探索成就系统和画廊，重温你最精彩的游戏瞬间，欣赏你在冒险过程中解锁的所有视听素材。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2403600/extras/fc36f1353aa99adce8d42ea7c91883b5.webp?t=1758814196\" width=616 height=40 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2403600/extras/d73548e25be2a9c68717c0508f796cb9.poster.avif?t=1758814196\" width=700 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2403600/extras/d73548e25be2a9c68717c0508f796cb9.webm?t=1758814196\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2403600/extras/756f3ad9b6fd20f25646c5cff7927a9e.webp?t=1758814196\" width=370 height=48 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Jamboy只是一个友善的果酱小子。他话不多，所以我们对他的了解几乎都来自他的行动。他似乎有点容易被左右——他的好Billy总能轻松说服他参与各种恶作剧。也许他其实认同这些计划……又或者，他只是太害羞，不敢说“不”。他会在某个时刻学会划清界限吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2403600/extras/af3d24c50f4e020d4f87ad97d27ac55a.webp?t=1758814196\" width=370 height=48 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Billy是个彻头彻尾的叛逆者。年轻时，他总是故意和别人唱反调。他喜欢偷东西、逃避警察……至少他的交友软件简介是这么写的，也许他只是想显得“狠”一点。他还是个十足的操控狂，总是威胁他的好朋友Jamboy，逼他参与那些扭曲的计划。总的来说，他不是个讨人喜欢的家伙——但奇怪的是，你会慢慢对他产生某种“习惯性好感”。</p>",
